snippet.title: 2021 Summer Academy Blooming Artists Concert #2
snippet.description:
Cheer on the students of ENCORE's 2021 Online Academy as they perform their solo repertoire!

Elle Cho - Camille Saint Saens (1835-1921): Violin Concerto No. 3, I. Allegro non troppo. Milana Pavchinskaya, piano.

Nathan Lau - Felix Mendelssohn (1809 - 1847): Violin Concerto in E minor, Op. 64, I. Allegro molto appassionato. Geoffrey Conquer, piano.

Seoyun Oh - Johannes Brahms (1833 - 1897): Viola Sonata Op.120 No. 2 E flat Major, I. Allegro amabile. Jungeun Choi, Piano.

Caroline Cornell - J.S. Bach (1685-1750): Violin Sonata No. 1 in G minor, II. Fuga.

Amina Knapp - J.S. Bach: Violin Sonata no. 1 in G minor, III. Siciliana.

Jacqueline Rodenbeck - J. S. Bach: Violin Sonata No. 2 in A minor, II. Fuga.

Chloe Schwartz - J.S. Bach: Violin Sonata No. 2 in A Minor, III. Andante.

Yu-Ming (Andrew) Ma - Eugène Ysaÿe (1858-1931): Violin Sonata No. 3 in D minor, Ballade.

Yeram Lee - Robert Schumann (1810-1856): Märchenbilder, op. 113, I. Nicht schnell, II. Lebhaft, III. Rasch. Soo Mi Yim, piano.

Adrian Jackson - Max Reger (1873-1916): Suite No. 1 in G minor for Solo Viola, I. Molto Sostenuto.

Celia Morin - Felix Mendelssohn (1809 - 1847): Violin Concerto in E minor, Op. 64, III. Allegretto non troppo – Allegro molto vivace. Sylvia Bruns, piano.

Kiarra Saito-Beckman - Eugène Ysaÿe: Sonata for Solo Violin, Op. 27, No. 2 "Jacques Thibaud", I. Obsession – Prelude: Poco vivace, II. Malinconia – Poco lento, III. Danse des ombres – Sarabande (Lento), IV. Les Furies – Allegro furioso.
